\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand formatted
reference "sub:Selling-shares"

\end_inset

).
\end_layout

\end_deeper
\begin_layout Enumerate
Shares equaling 10% of the company, or 1 share (whichever is the larger)
 are placed in the bank pool from the treasury without recompense to the
 company.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Enumerate
If the company increased its share-count to more than the next larger size
 (see 
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand formatted
reference "tab:Company-Sizes"

\end_inset

):
\end_layout

\begin_deeper
\begin_layout Itemize
Shares equal to an additional 10% of the company are placed in the bank
 pool without recompense to the company.
\end_layout

\end_deeper
\end_deeper
\end_deeper
\begin_layout Itemize
